{"tid":2109660,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華禁洛歇馬丁報復對台售武","createTime":"2020-07-15T11:14:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-15T11:42:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"825f009ab213a4b69eb2fa008c7219b59663018a","tid":2109660,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T11:14:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200715/HZ2247K7UAZEZN3CTGVY6ARG4M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200715%2FHZ2247K7UAZEZN3CTGVY6ARG4M%2F&d=Qf9F%2BOyPnpVTj1ufbg5Gu8g7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=ea571525\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200715%2FHZ2247K7UAZEZN3CTGVY6ARG4M%2F&h=b918dea1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200715/HZ2247K7UAZEZN3CTGVY6ARG4M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n華禁洛歇馬丁報復對台售武<br />\n<br />\n美國早前對台提供價值6.2億美元（約48億港元）的對台軍售案，中國外交部昨宣佈制裁美國軍火業巨擘洛歇馬丁（Lockheed Martin）反擊。不過台灣軍事專家亓樂義指，美軍火絕少出售予中國，中國進口軍火多來自俄羅斯，中美軍火規格、保養方式等不一樣，故制裁效果有限。<br />\n<br />\n洛歇馬丁是全球最大國防工業承包商之一，產品包括雷達、軍用運輸機等。外交部。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Qk6LrKl8EIOR7zDcUmFPGtqBvv0=/585x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SEUUPZ64SA5BYOTAP4ZFF3KJTM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQk6LrKl8EIOR7zDcUmFPGtqBvv0%3D%2F585x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSEUUPZ64SA5BYOTAP4ZFF3KJTM.gif&h=463e5a46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n克魯茲<br />\n(motherlode)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n克魯茲戲稱遊中伊泡湯<br />\n<br />\n國台辦批評民進黨「以武謀獨」不會得逞，只會給台灣人民帶來更大災難。台。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中國外交部前日宣佈制裁三名美國國會議員等，反制美方懲治新疆高官。遭中國點名制裁的共和黨參議員克魯茲（Ted Cruz）表示，北京顯然被美方懲治嚇壞，戲稱本打算遊。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/中央社"},{"pid":"9609c8d4126670ea875363b6db05f4d48248b254","tid":2109660,"uid":16057,"like":0,"dislike